name: Dixie - Coors Light
description: Dixie(not her real name, but the name she used when we shot some fetish content much later) was a friend of a friend who was randomly down for a road trip out to the Salton Sea to shoot some photos. Of course, this was in the middle of Summer and none of us rockets scientists had thought about the 110F heat and stench of Salton Sea that time of year. After maybe an hour the decision was made to call it quits and head for the nearest town where we could find a motel next to a bar. That happened to be Indio, CA and it was a million times better than suffering at the Salton Sea. The bar was straight out of a movie kind of crazy and the motel was straight out of a David Lynch movie crazy. Great combination. We partied all day and night(the pool was open 24/7) for three days. All of that is to say that this is Dixie drinking a Coors in a bikini at some ungodly hour of the morning at a shitty motel in Indio, CA.
